snippet.title: Zombieland: Hot Girl Zombie Attack (AMBER HEARD HALLOWEEN MOVIE SCENE)
snippet.description:
Columbus is living the dream! Or is he? 🥴 Columbus's hot neighbor shows up on his doorstep to protect herself from a homeless cannibal that tried to bite her. Turns out, she did, in fact, get bitten 😬😬😬
#Zombieland #JesseEisenberg #AmberHeard

Watch the full movie: https://play.google.com/store/movies/details/Zombieland?id=F_FncB-OSic

Nerdy college student Columbus (Jesse Eisenberg) has survived the plague that has turned mankind into flesh-devouring zombies because he’s scared of just about everything. Gun-toting, Twinkie-loving Tallahassee (Woody Harrelson) has no fears. Together, they are about to stare down their most horrifying challenge yet: each other’s company. Emma Stone and Abigail Breslin co-star in this double-hitting, head-smashing comedy.
